        <mj-column width="65%">
          <mj-text>
            <a href="https://communitycycles.org/about/">Community Cycles</a> has organized more than 60 local businesses in Boulder to host breakfast and bike service stations to serve food and drinks for commuters on <strong>June 28th</strong> for <strong>Bike to Work Day</strong> from 6:30 to 9 a.m. KGNU is one of the breakfast stations!  Come win tickets to a concert or an annual membership and go on a tour to see how what you hear on air is made.<br><br>Ride (or walk) by our Boulder station at 4700 Walnut St. for breakfast June 28th, we’d love to see you!
          </mj-text>
